<br>
I had sort of mixxed experiences with it.  It's not in my opinion better for holding aggro than using a dual wield setup, but it's not much worse if at all except as you note, at the start which can be an issue also with slower 2h weapons.<br>
<br>
I'd recommend leading in with dual wield, and then depending on the situation you can swap then or sometimes I wouldn't swap until my disc faded.<br>
<br>
